NAME
    App::sibs - Simple incremental backup system

VERSION
    0.01

SYNOPSIS
      $ sibs;
      $ sibs setup;
      $ sibs run;

DESCRIPTION
    "sibs" create backups from your source system to a destination server,
    using "rsync".

